Class ObservationWithData

java.lang.Object
  gov.noaa.ncdc.crn.domain.ObservationWithData
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<ObservationWithData>
public class ObservationWithData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ObservationWithData>

ObservationWithData is a wrapper class which associates an Observation to a Map containing some or all of its observed and/or calculated values.

public java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,ElementValue> getElementValues()
